<p class="p1">&lt;body&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;h1&gt;Confidance&lt;/h1&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Move. Connect. Feel confident.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>Confidance is a space for people to connect through music, movement, fitness, and friendship.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>We create a welcoming environment where everyone can feel comfortable, supported, and empowered.</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;h2&gt;What We Offer&lt;/h2&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>• Yoga classes&lt;br&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>• Barre classes&lt;br&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>• Dance classes&lt;br&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>• Corporate yoga sessions&lt;br&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>• Workshops &amp; special events</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;h2&gt;Our Mission&lt;/h2&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;p&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">    </span>Our goal is to help you feel stronger, more confident, and more connected—both physically and mentally.</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;/p&gt;</p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;h2&gt;Contact&lt;/h2&gt;</p>
<p class="p1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>&lt;p&gt;Email: your@email.com&lt;/p&gt;</p>
